Package: RScythica
Type: Package
Title: Access to external data sets via memory mapped files
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-03-26
Author: Gerald Hewes <gerald@geraldthewes.org>
Maintainer: Gerald Hewes <gerald@geraldthewes.org>
Description: Maps externally created data sets in R, allowing for analysis of
    data sets larger than the systems memory. Datasets are split into
    partitions and slits to allow for scale
License: LGPL-2.1
Imports:
    methods,
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    Rcpp,
    iterators,
    foreach
RcppModules: rscythica
Suggests:
    testthat
